<section id='DefaultLayers'>
<title>DefaultLayers</title>

<cmdsynopsis>
	<command>DefaultLayers</command
	><arg choice='plain'
		><replaceable>bottom</replaceable
	></arg
	><arg choice='plain'
		><replaceable>put</replaceable
	></arg
	><arg choice='plain'
		><replaceable>top</replaceable
	></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>

<para>
Changes the layers that are used for the
<fvwmref cmd="Style" opt="StaysOnBottom"/>,
<fvwmref cmd="Style" opt="StaysPut"/>,
<fvwmref cmd="Style" opt="StaysOnTop"/>
<fvwmref cmd="Style"/>
options.  Initially, the layers 2, 4 and 6 are used.</para>

</section>
